<surveypage sre_1>
/ caption = "We are interested in your experiences with racism. As you answer the questions below, please think about your ENTIRE LIFE, from when you were a child to the present.

For each question, please select the number (1-6) that best captures the things that have happened to you. 

Answer each question TWICE, once for what has happened to your IN THE PAST YEAR, and once for what YOUR ENTIRE LIFE HAS BEEN LIKE.

Use these numbers:
Select '1' = If this has NEVER happened to you
Select '2' = If this has happened ONCE IN A WHILE (less than 10% of the time)
Select '3' = If this has happened SOMETIMES (10%-25% of the time)
Select '4' = If this has happened A LOT (26%-49% of the time)
Select '5' = If this has happened MOST OF THE TIME (50%-70% of the time)
Select '6' = If this has happened ALMOST ALL THE TIME (more than 70% of the time)"

